<p><a href="https://twitter.com/_wilfredh">Wilfred Hughes</a> has a handy <a href="https://twitter.com/_wilfredh/status/659499112677642242?refsrc%3Demail&amp;s%3D11">tip</a> to bail you out of a hung Emacs instance:</p>
<pre><code class="language-{.bash">pkill -SIGUSR2 emacs
</code></pre>
